mersion environment. There are three options to learn English: software, audio CDs and English exercises on an iPod.","You view and listen to videos of native English speakers in real-life situations. There are also audio conversations to which you listen to learn English, and a flash card system to reinforce what you have learned. Berlitz English Premier lets you practice conversations and records your voice to help you improve your English pronunciation.","This ESL application offers English exercises for beginners, intermediate and advanced learners. Beginners learn English greetings, introductions, numbers and travel phrases as well as instruction in shopping, sightseeing and other basics. Intermediate English learners study and practice speech on dining and restaurants, hotels and travel, emergencies and the environment. Advanced learners are given English exercises and conversational practice on an evening out with friends and survival phrases, as well as office and telephone conversations.","Berlitz English Premier offers speech analysis to help you learn English and speak like a native English speaker. The tool lets you record and play back your speech to compare it to native-English pronunciations and improve your pronunciation.","Berlitz has a noted history of success in teaching languages to business and government representatives, as well as for personal use. We don&#39;t dispute the merits of immersion in learning to speak English if it&#39;s not your native language. However, Berlitz English Premier lacks a few features and tools offered by its competitors.","It does not offer instruction in English grammar or writing. It lacks a word processing converter, dictionary, glossary, and word and root search. Though it&#39;s not imperative, the product does not have a companion book."]},"id":"7f5074f7-0361-4b07-ab11-d6f188c79a1a","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"c1cab0bb-a8e2-4f17-bfc0-5f052223fe2c","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Be